        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, reboil half a kettle</p><p>Slice your <strong>cucumber</strong> into discs</p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>",
