    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 1 <strong>roti </strong>per person<strong> </strong>to a baking tray (or two!) and top<strong> </strong>with the<strong> grated cheese</strong>, <strong>remaining chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Place the <strong>remaining rotis</strong> on top so you end up with roti sandwiches</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 6-8 min or until the cheese is melted – this is your <strong>Malaysian-style cheesy roti canai</strong></p>",
