    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>Malaysian-style cheesy roti canai</strong> into quarters</p><p>Serve the <strong>lentil & chickpea dal</strong> (discard the lemongrass!) with the <strong>quartered Malaysian-style cheesy roti canai </strong>and <strong>quick-pickled chilli cucumber </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
